<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />明天怎么还不到呀～</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的生日，<delay20 />
