	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道吗，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天可是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的
生日哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我准备了非常特别的礼物呢。<delay frames="40" />
