我决定要笑着送别<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也不要留下遗憾哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
